{"tid":872421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係咪多數都燥底？係咪一個惡性循環？","createTime":"2018-10-22T16:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T17:10:48.000Z","uid":39496,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a774d5e73ae5686ee5984a22b8f1209766a7b7b3","tid":872421,"uid":39496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"如題 大家有冇諗過呢個問題？<br />\n<br />\n出街留心唔難發覺 <br />\n<br />\n大部分人都好燥 陌生人互相充滿敵意 <br />\n<br />\n越多人既地方越嚴重<br />\n<br />\n各自既保護意識超強 全部起晒鋼  可以隨時開火開拖<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪香港太迫大太壓力先係咁？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人諗過長此下去會否成為一個惡性循環？<br />\n<br />\n到最後人既關係會發展成點？<br />\n<br />\n定係只係杞人憂天 其實只會維持現狀唔會惡化？<br />\n<br />\n咁落去乜真係唔會爆煲咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中性 》冷漠 》無視  》敵對  之後呢？"},{"pid":"e09d399613f8641d660f5d5a703420ce9c6e2b8d","tid":872421,"uid":39496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"純有感而發 歡迎討論"},{"pid":"181ae581b078418f10826ca9ab6337f00ca54379","tid":872421,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦港豬打兩野就認輸"},{"pid":"eef9ff6311c53de9076b67997525d074ee9a5e3e","tid":872421,"uid":50872,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"次次落親街人多到行唔到<br />\n唔燥就難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa350d35dc8ce0f2de70263b4661f307369b306","tid":872421,"uid":86345,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"某程度上係係煌國人做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969a0d30f98cb32740cf722c287045fd1b9cc7b7","tid":872421,"uid":118463,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"eef9ff6311c53de9076b67997525d074ee9a5e3e","tid":872421,"uid":50872,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"次次落親街人多到行唔到<br />\n唔燥就難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:26:11.